      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "UNCHARTERED (5) skirted wide from an outside draw and found the front, leading until late when second (30.83) at this track in a Grade 6 over 530m. Likely to feature again. ZINFANDEL PEARL (1) is a first starter from the Cherylee Barber yard by Fernando Bale out of Zinfandel Nikki. Drawn well and should get her chance. Market moves likely to signal ability but profiles strongly for this. COMPTON ROCKS (2) struggled to get involved last start at Mt Gambier, but prior to that won by 2 lengths at Mt Gambier (30.08) beating Reiko Comet in a Special conditions race on May 3. Boasts two wins from two starts out of this box. Bold showing expected. LIL REX (8) generally performs well here at this distance.",
